Package org.lappsgrid.discriminator

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Discriminator
    Discriminator objects are used to provide type information about Data objects passed between LAPPS services.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DiscriminatorRegistry
    The DiscriminatorRegistry serves as the source of all knowledge for Discriminator objects.
    Helpers
    Helper methods to get Discriminator values from Data objects.
    Types
    Static final definitions of the most commonly used discriminator types.
    Uri
    Static final definitions of the URI of the most commonly used discriminators.
